age\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1080, \"end\": 1089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_Peng_(basketball)\", \"score\": 0.9999984532281044, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zhou Peng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_Peng_(basketball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_Peng_(basketball)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"his race\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"his leg\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years ago, Great Britain's Thomas Young dominated this race but he cut a dejected figure here after missing a bronze by just one hundredth of a second.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1150, \"end\": 1163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998551437545964, \"rank\": 0.00014487722882651415, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1166, \"end\": 1178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Yonge\", \"score\": 0.9997177931501757, \"rank\": 0.00028000713648087963, \"text\": \"Thomas Young\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Yonge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Yonge\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this race\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"a dejected figure\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"a second\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was not a single American in the field in Tokyo but with the Los Angeles Games on the horizon, the US Olympic and Paralympic Committee decided something needed to be done and fast.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1315, \"end\": 1323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9344006647815355, \"rank\": 0.04787362632382129, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.7498012774830219, \"rank\": 0.3336866738253657, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1359, \"end\": 1370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999991528057, \"rank\": 8.471795387303545e-10, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1397, \"end\": 1399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999939405599301, \"rank\": 6.059209146489493e-06, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"the horizon\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The prospect of not being competitive in the blue-riband events at their home Games was simply not palatable and a talent identification programme was quickly initiated, with three finalists here the result and Blackwell's transition from High School football star to track and field rewarded.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1691, \"end\": 1700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Blackwell\", \"score\": 0.9998948905232546, \"rank\": 0.00010512052513908959, \"text\": \"Blackwell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Blackwell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Blackwell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The prospect\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"the blue-riband events\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"their home\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1557}, {\"ngram\": \"Games\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"a talent identification programme\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"three finalists\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"High School football star\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was the perfect race, but I was just focused on what I had to do and get to the line as fast as possible,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the perfect race\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was just telling myself to get out fast, do what you got to do.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just got into drive phase, stood up tall and started chugging it.\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drive phase\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It felt like it was a little bit slow.\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2070, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I looked at the line as I crossed the screen and saw 10.64 (seconds) I was thinking 'OK, alright, let us go'.\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"the screen\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"(seconds\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had to bring something over here to put a little pizzazz into things.\\\"\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"a little pizzazz\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Defending British sprint champions Young and Sophie Hahn were both left scratching their heads after being blown away by world records.\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2272, \"end\": 2279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9999984920552835, \"rank\": 1.480368252058758e-06, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 2307, \"end\": 2318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Hahn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sophie Hahn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Hahn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Hahn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Young\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"their heads\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2356}, {\"ngram\": \"world records\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They arrived at the Stade de France as the ones to beat but quickly discovered the rest of the world had simply caught them up.\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2434}, {\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Americans have scouted athletes from other sports and they are doing such a good job to bring these guys in for LA,\\\" said Young, whose season's best would have earned him silver.\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2529, \"end\": 2542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1290346394937024e-23, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"other sports\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"such a good job\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2617}, {\"ngram\": \"these guys\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2647}, {\"ngram\": \"Young\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2660}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Beating them at their home is the ambition now but I am gutted, it's been my best season ever and this is just a totally horrible feeling.\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their home\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"the ambition\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"my best season\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2802}, {\"ngram\": \"just a totally horrible feeling\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My leg cramped up in the call room but no excuses, it just wasn't my night.\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My leg\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"the call room\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2889}, {\"ngram\": \"my night\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have got off the track injury free, the tears will dry and I can focus on the future.\\\"\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 3019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track injury\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"the tears\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2978}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two-time champion Hahn, the second quickest qualifier to the final, did not make the podium.\", \"from\": 3021, \"to\": 3113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3039, \"end\": 3043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reynaldo_Hahn\", \"score\": 0.9910263112055625, \"rank\": 0.008862779265464502, \"text\": \"Hahn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reynaldo_Hahn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reynaldo_Hahn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She trailed home a distant sixth as Colombia's Karen Palomeque Moreno did not just snatch her title but carved over a tenth of a second off her world record, clocking 12.26 secs to win gold.\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3151, \"end\": 3159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9947967339584495, \"rank\": 0.005230434320993558, \"text\": \"Colombia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3162, \"end\": 3167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Carpenter\", \"score\": 0.9910261454927672, \"rank\": 0.00904372876377668, \"text\": \"Karen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Carpenter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Carpenter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her title\", \"from\": 3205, \"to\": 3214}, {\"ngram\": \"a tenth\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3238}, {\"ngram\": \"a second\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3250}, {\"ngram\": \"her world record\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3271}, {\"ngram\": \"12.26 secs\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3292}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the 38 class has got really competitive which is great for the sport but I am obviously still gutted,\\\" she insisted.\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 38 class\", \"from\": 3316, \"to\": 3328}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been running a long time; I have achieved what I wanted to achieve and it's time to enjoy it really.\\\"\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"David Weir has also been at it a long time, though competing at his seventh Paralympics does not always give the best impression he is having fun.\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"David Weir\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3554}, {\"ngram\": \"his seventh Paralympics\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3631}, {\"ngram\": \"the best impression\", \"from\": 3653, \"to\": 3672}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 3686, \"to\": 3689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Weir is best known for his London 2012 heroics, proving unstoppable to win four golds in just seven days, but his last two Paralympics have seen him cut a glum figure, returning from both Rio and Tokyo empty headed.\", \"from\": 3692, \"to\": 3907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3719, \"end\": 3730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 0.9996225252365394, \"rank\": 0.00037761730468178817, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Paralympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3880, \"end\": 3883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999181455, \"